# Radar Chart - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/radarchart/

# Radar Chart

![Screenshot](../img/radar/radarchart.jpg) _A Radar Map_

## Set up

  1. Define a data source and select _chart type_ to create.

  2. Select _Radar Columns_ for the category data.

  3. Add a Layer and define the _Series Data_ to plot.

## Basics

![Screenshot](../img/radar/radarbasics.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Chart Type_

    Dropdown selection between: `radar`, `polarArea` and `pie`.
_Data Source_

    A [data source](../datasources/).
_Focus_

    A [View State Parameter](../viewstateparameters/) for [linking components](../viewstateparameters/#linking-components).
_Selected Value_

_Selected Value Attribute_

_Selected Row ViewState Routing_

    To capture clicks on the chart 

[Selected values](../viewstateparameters/#selected-values)

## Data

![Screenshot](../img/radar/dataradar.jpg)

_Radar Columns_

    Select from [data source](../datasources/) or [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/); values represent radar labels. 
_GridLine color_

_AngleLine color_

_Gridline Opacity_

_AngleLine Opacity_

    

Define radar color and opacity line. Opacity is a value between 0 and 100.

### Layers

**Layer 1**

_Data_

    Determine which data column is charted.
_Color_

_Border Color_

_Use color Palette_

_Radar Color Opacity_

    Set area and border color of radar.
_Display Name_

    Descriptive name of data layer (label in chart).
_Point Style_

_Point Radius_

    Define criteria of radar points. Select from `circle`, `cross`, `crossRot`, `dash`, `line`, `rect`, `rectRounded`, `rectRot`, `star`, and `triangle`.

## Legend

_Show_

    Toggle display of legend.
_LabelColor_

    Set legend font color.
_Position_

    Place legend `top`, `bottom`, `left` and `right`.

## Chart padding

![Screenshot](../img/radar/chartpadding.jpg)

_Left_

_Right_

_Top_

_Bottom_

    Assigns internal pixel padding.

## Ticks

Controls radar internal grid labels.

_Display_

    Toggle display of tick labels.
_Font Color_

_Font Size_

    Define color and size of tick labels.
_Show Label Backdrop_

    Adds white space around labels, improving clarity.
_Backdrop Color_

_Backdrop Padding X and Y_

    Sets radar tick label color and area padding.
_Max Ticks Limit_

    

Sets number of radar zones.

![Screenshot](../img/radar/radartick3.jpg)

_Begin at Zero_

    Central point of radar starts at zero versus best fit.
_Format_

    Select from `General`, `Number`, `Smart Number`, `Formatted Number`, `Datetime`.
_Decimal Places_

    Where `Number`, `Smart Number`, `Formatted Number` is selected, set number of Decimal Places to use.
_Hide Trailing Zeroes_

    Doesn't display trailing zeroes in a number.
_Date/Time Format_

    Set date type when `Datetime` is selected.
_Prefix_

_Suffix_

    Apply text label, e.g.: "%", "Â£", "$".
_Radar Labels Size_

    Set font size of outer radar labels.

![Screenshot](../img/radar/radartooltio.jpg)

_Stack Tooltip Data_

    When checked, it will subtract current level from previous level to return a differential.

[Custom tooltips](../template/#custom-tooltips)

[Tooltip Helper](../template/#select-helper)

## Color palette

Define when radar chart uses [OLAP/Pivot data](../datasources/#pivot-query).

## Animations

![Screenshot](../img/radar/piechartanimations.jpg)

_Enabled_

    When checked offers smoothing render animation.

